30 Department of Education, subject to the following qualifications:
31 (A) Subject to the limitations of subparagraph (B) of this paragraph, all otherwise valid
32 rules adopted by the State Board of Education and Department of Education prior to
33 January 1, 1990, are ratified and validated and shall be effective until January 1, 1991,
34 whether or not such rules were adopted in compliance with the requirements of this
35 chapter; and
36 (B) Effective January 1, 1991, any rule of the State Board of Education or Department
37 of Education which has not been proposed, submitted, and adopted in accordance with
38 the requirements of this chapter shall be void and of no effect."
39 SECTION 2.
40 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
